<dd>6. gently</dd><br>
<dd>가볍게 눈웃음을 치는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of smiling with one's eyes lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>7. smoothly</dd><br>
<dd>얽힌 실 등이 잘 풀리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of tangled thread, etc., disentangling easily.</dd><br>
<dt>살살 [살살]</dt><br>
